 records, while the vernacular form <i>Maud</i> was the one in everyday use. <i>Matilda</i> was revived in England as a learned form in the 18th century."]},{"name":"Mechtilde","meanings":["from <i>maht</i>, <i>meht</i> ‘might’ + <i>hild</i> ‘battle’."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Mathilde de Houdetot was born in 1197, in Houdetot, Seine-Maritime, Normandy, France. She had at least 1 son with Robert IV de Courcy - Baron de Courcy. She died in 1249, in Courcy, Calvados, Normandy, France, at the age of 52."},"et":{"1197–1249":"1197–1249","1186–1239":"1186–1239","1229–1289":"1229–1289","1239":"1239","1249":"1249","1289":"1289","1197":"1197","1186":"1186","1229":"1229","Houdetot, Seine-Maritime, Normandy, France":"Houdetot, Seine-Maritime, Normandie, Prantsusmaa","Courcy, Calvados, Normandy, France":"Courcy, Calvados, Normandie, Prantsusmaa"},"fi":{"1197–1249":"1197–1249","1186–1239":"1186–1239","1229–1289":"1229–1289","1239":"1239","1249":"1249","1289":"1289","1197":"1197","1186":"1186","1229":"1229","Houdetot, Seine-Maritime, Normandy, France":"Houdetot, Seine-Maritime, Normandie, Ranska","Courcy, Calvados, Normandy, France":"Courcy, Calvados, Normandie, Ranska"},"fr":{"1197–1249":"1197–1249","1186–1239":"1186–1239","1229–1289":"1229–1289","1239":"1239","1249":"1249","1289":"1289","1197":"1197","1186":"1186","1229":"1229","Houdetot, Seine-Maritime, Normandy, France":"Houdetot, Seine-Maritime, Normandie, France","Courcy, Calvados, Normandy, France":"Courcy, Calvados, Normandie, France","lifeSummary":"Mathilde de Houdetot est née en 1197, à Houdetot, Seine-Maritime, Normandie, France. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Robert IV de Courcy - Baron de Courcy. Elle est décédée en 1249, à Courcy, Calvados, Normandie, France, à l’âge de 52 ans."},"de":{"1197–1249":"1197–1249","1186–1239":"1186–1239","1229–1289":"1229–1289","1239":"1239","1249":"1249","1289":"1289","1197":"1197","1186":"1186","1229":"1229","Houdetot, Seine-Maritime, Normandy, France":"Houdetot, Seine-Maritime, Normandie, 